{"tid":958782,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"情緒病同精神病睇中醫有冇用？","createTime":"2018-12-28T06:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T06:23:08.000Z","uid":123430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5c5e71447fef22657546de3ad2a640292611460b","tid":958782,"uid":123430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T06:02:17.000Z","msg":"我屋企人一直都好吹捧中醫 講到中醫能醫百病<br />\n但我覺得中醫同西醫各有出色既地方<br />\n<br />\n而且我認為 神經，精神病同情緒病 中醫係醫唔到，因為呢d地方始終要用藥物去控制 中醫係調理唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇人 熟中醫或者睇中醫 醫好我所講既病？"},{"pid":"4733a6e796185e9c3c6397158f1af1f8d4be0fcc","tid":958782,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T06:02:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92478545b579421d9023390cc78b2cbcd2377f4a","tid":958782,"uid":170068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T06:04:19.000Z","msg":"因腎虧導致精神失常<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9ea5207fd9ebf6cb6b41cb4e95b9a02e6f7b42","tid":958782,"uid":227322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T06:05:23.000Z","msg":"中醫：心病還需心藥醫"},{"pid":"b30b38f7dde9cf66355b61a00e719e815a9c76ad","tid":958782,"uid":200270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T06:06:10.000Z","msg":"針灸?"},{"pid":"14af11e64215e2376e3ed5a7b8c34d5c44a58df3","tid":958782,"uid":123430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92478545b579421d9023390cc78b2cbcd2377f4a","tid":958782,"uid":170068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T06:04:19.000Z","msg":"因腎虧導致精神失常<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T06:16:03.000Z","msg":"抑鬱症患者會情緒低落、覺得自己一無是處、甚至有自殺傾向，在中醫角度，此症是肝經絡問題，因心、肝、脾三臟受累及氣血失調而引起；焦慮症是指患者無時無刻對任何事情都有難以控制的憂慮，中醫的解說是因心膽問題，由於心、膽、脾等功能失調引起；而驚恐症的患者會無時無刻感到害怕和不安，中醫認為是由於心、肝、脾、腎問題而引致。<br />\n<br />\n啫係精神創傷同心理壓力唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a50d35771de7007046ed01dc49984fc6582c19","tid":958782,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T06:23:08.000Z","msg":"你俾一千萬我，即刻唔抑鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個人覺得環境、際遇先係最大影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}